ss=\"v\">320W</div></div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"panel\">\n          <div class=\"ph\">\n            <h3>Customer mood</h3>\n            <span class=\"ph-sub\">// 3 accounts</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"mood-body\">\n            <div class=\"mood-ring\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\">\n                <circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"42\" stroke=\"#1e2338\" stroke-width=\"10\" fill=\"none\"/>\n                <circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"42\" stroke=\"#34d399\" stroke-width=\"10\" fill=\"none\"\n                        stroke-dasharray=\"264\" stroke-dashoffset=\"146\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n              </svg>\n              <div class=\"center\">\n                <div>\n                  <div class=\"big\">+45</div>\n                  <div class=\"lbl\">net mood</div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"mood-list\">\n              <div class=\"row\">\n                <span>Devon Park</span>\n                <div class=\"b\"><i class=\"good\" style=\"width: 92%\"></i></div>\n                <span class=\"v\">+88</span>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"row\">\n                <span>Mira (lead)</span>\n                <div class=\"b\"><i class=\"ok\" style=\"width: 56%\"></i></div>\n                <span class=\"v\">+22</span>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"row\">\n                <span>Karen H.</span>\n                <div class=\"b\"><i class=\"bad\" style=\"width: 18%; margin-left: auto\"></i></div>\n                <span class=\"v\">−42</span>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"row\">\n                <span>Anon (trial)</span>\n                <div class=\"b\"><i class=\"warn\" style=\"width: 40%\"></i></div>\n                <span class=\"v\">?</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n      </div>\n\n      <!-- Tickets -->\n      <section class=\"panel tickets-panel\">\n        <div class=\"ph\">\n          <h3>Open tickets</h3>\n          <span class=\"ph-sub\">// 3 unassigned</span>\n          <div class=\"ph-right\">\n            <a class=\"more\">Inbox →</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"tickets-body\">\n          <div class=\"ticket-row\">\n            <div class=\"av av-K\">K</div>\n            <div class=\"info\">\n              <div class=\"who\">Karen Holloway <span class=\"org\">@ nutricoach.io</span></div>\n              <div class=\"msg\">\"This is the THIRD time my checkout has 500'd. I have receipts and screenshots.\"</div>\n            </div>\n            <span class=\"sev p1\">P1</span>\n            <span class=\"age\">11m</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"ticket-row\">\n            <div class=\"av av-A\">A</div>\n            <div class=\"info\">\n              <div class=\"who\">Anon <span class=\"org\">@ ?? · burner</span></div>\n              <div class=\"msg\">\"do you log egress. paying in crypto. say no and I delete this account.\"</div>\n            </div>\n            <span class=\"sev p2\">P2</span>\n            <span class=\"age\">1h</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"ticket-row\">\n            <div class=\"av av-D\">D</div>\n            <div class=\"info\">\n              <div class=\"who\">Devon Park <span class=\"org\">@ pixelbrew</span></div>\n              <div class=\"msg\">\"Loving the dashboard btw — small q on usage caps and overage billing.\"</div>\n            </div>\n            <span class=\"sev p3\">P3</span>\n            <span class=\"age\">3h</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <!-- Finance -->\n      <section class=\"panel finance-panel\">\n        <div class=\"ph\">\n          <h3>Cash flow · 14 days</h3>\n          <span class=\"ph-sub\">// projection dashed</span>\n          <div class=\"ph-right\">\n            <a class=\"more\">Finance →</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"finance-body\">\n          <div class=\"chart-wrap\">\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 400 200\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\">\n              <!-- grid -->\n              <g stroke=\"#1e2338\" stroke-width=\"1\">\n                <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"40\"/>\n                <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"80\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"80\"/>\n                <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"120\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"120\"/>\n                <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"160\" x2=\"400\" y2=\"160\"/>\n              </g>\n              <!-- area history -->\n              <path d=\"M 0,150 L 30,160 L 60,145 L 90,140 L 120,120 L 150,125 L 180,115 L 210,100 L 240,80 L 270,75 L 300,60 L 300,200 L 0,200 Z\"\n                    fill=\"rgba(99,102,241,.15)\"/>\n              <!-- line history -->\n              <polyline points=\"0,150 30,160 60,145 90,140 120,120 150,125 180,115 210,100 240,80 270,75 300,60\"\n                        stroke=\"#818cf8\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\"/>\n              <!-- projection -->\n              <polyline points=\"300,60 330,55 360,52 400,48\"\n                        stroke=\"#f59e0b\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"4 4\" fill=\"none\"/>\n              <!-- today marker -->\n              <line x1=\"300\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"300\" y2=\"200\" stroke=\"#262c46\" stroke-dasharray=\"2 3\"/>\n              <circle cx=\"300\" cy=\"60\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#f59e0b\" stroke=\"#0e1220\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n              <text x=\"304\" y=\"48\" fill=\"#f59e0b\" font-family=\"JetBrains Mono\" font-size=\"10\">TODAY · $390</text>\n              <text x=\"0\" y=\"195\" fill=\"#5d6483\" font-family=\"JetBrains Mono\" font-size=\"10\">Day -14</text>\n              <text x=\"370\" y=\"195\" fill=\"#5d6483\" font-family=\"JetBrains Mono\" font-size=\"10\">+14d</text>\n            </svg>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"chart-stats\">\n            <div class=\"fstat\">\n              <div class=\"k\">Daily income</div>\n              <div class=\"v\">$60.00 <small class=\"up\">+12%</small></div>\n              <div class=\"meta\">From 3 paying accounts</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"fstat\">\n              <div class=\"k\">Daily burn</div>\n              <div class=\"v\">$15.00 <small class=\"dn\">+0%</small></div>\n              <div class=\"meta\">Power · domain · 1 colo unit</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"fstat\">\n              <div class=\"k\">Projected (14d)</div>\n              <div class=\"v\">$1,020 <small class=\"up\">+162%</small></div>\n              <div class=\"meta\">If churn stays at 0%</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <!-- Era -->\n      <section class=\"panel era-panel\">\n        <div class=\"ph\">\n          <h3>Era progress</h3>\n          <span class=\"ph-sub\">// unlock Era 2 — Colo</span>\n          <div class=\"ph-right\">\n            <a class=\"more\">Tech tree →</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"era-body\">\n          <div class=\"era-hero\">\n            <div class=\"era-badge\">1</div>\n            <div>\n              <div class=\"name\">Garage Era</div>\n              <div class=\"sub\">One beige tower, your cousin's wifi, ambition.</div>\n              <div class=\"year\">2026 · Day 12 / ≈90</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"era-req\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Requirements for Era 2</div>\n            <div class=\"req done\">\n              <div class=\"check\"></div>\n              <div class=\"lbl\">Sign first paying customer <small>complete · Day 4</small></div>\n              <div class=\"prog\"><b>1</b>/1</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"req\">\n              <div class=\"check\"></div>\n              <div class=\"lbl\">Reach <b>$500 cash</b> on hand</div>\n              <div class=\"prog\"><b>$390</b>/$500</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"req\">\n              <div class=\"check\"></div>\n              <div class=\"lbl\">Maintain SLA ≥ <b>99.5%</b> for 14 days</div>\n              <div class=\"prog\"><b>7</b>/14</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"req\">\n              <div class=\"check\"></div>\n              <div class=\"lbl\">Survive first P1 incident <small>currently triaging #042</small></div>\n              <div class=\"prog\"><b>0</b>/1</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"next-era\">\n            <div class=\"lock\">🔒</div>\n            <div class=\"name\">Era 2 · Colo</div>\n            <div class=\"sub\">Rent half a rack. Meet your first ISP. BGP. AS number.</div>\n            <div class=\"progress\"><i></i></div>\n            <div class=\"pct\">22% to unlock · ETA ~17 days</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <!-- Quick actions -->\n      <section class=\"panel quick-panel\">\n        <div class=\"ph\">\n          <h3>Quick actions</h3>\n          <span class=\"ph-sub\">// recommended for today</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"quick-body\">\n          <div class=\"quick buy\">\n            <div class=\"qico\">+</div>\n            <div class=\"body\">\n              <div class=\"title\">Buy server</div>\n              <div class=\"desc\">1U Pentium · 4GB · adds 1 slot</div>\n              <div class=\"price\">$180 · in stock</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"arrow\">→</div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"quick market\">\n            <div class=\"qico\">⚡</div>\n            <div class=\"body\">\n              <div class=\"title\">List on Marketplace</div>\n              <div class=\"desc\">Acquire 1-2 trial customers</div>\n              <div class=\"price\">$0 · 24h cooldown</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"arrow\">→</div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"quick hire\">\n            <div class=\"qico\">☰</div>\n            <div class=\"body\">\n              <div class=\"title\">Hire support agent</div>\n              <div class=\"desc\">Auto-triage P3 tickets</div>\n              <div class=\"price\">$80/wk · 🔒 Era 2</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"arrow\">→</div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"quick shift\">\n            <div class=\"qico\">▶</div>\n            <div class=\"body\">\n              <div class=\"title\">Start support shift</div>\n              <div class=\"desc\">30-min live ticket triage</div>\n              <div class=\"price\">+rep · +$ per ticket</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"arrow\">→</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <!-- Goals -->\n      <section class=\"panel goals-panel\">\n        <div class=\"ph\">\n          <h3>Weekly goals</h3>\n          <span class=\"ph-sub\">// resets in 3d 14h</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"goals-body\">\n          <div class=\"goal\">\n            <div>\n              <div class=\"gname\">Resolve 5 P1 tickets without refund</div>\n              <div class=\"gdesc\">2 of 5 resolved · don't lose Karen this time</div>\n              <div class=\"pbar\"><i style=\"width: 40%\"></i></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"reward\">+$100<small>+5 rep</small></div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"goal\">\n            <div>\n              <div class=\"gname\">Hit $50 MRR</div>\n              <div class=\"gdesc\">Currently $15 — upsell Devon or close Mira</div>\n              <div class=\"pbar\"><i style=\"width: 30%\"></i></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"reward\">+$200<small>blueprint</small></div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"goal\">\n            <div>\n              <div class=\"gname\">Zero unanswered tickets &gt; 6h</div>\n              <div class=\"gdesc\">3 unanswered now — oldest is 3h, you're fine</div>\n              <div class=\"pbar\"><i style=\"width: 70%\"></i></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"reward\">+10 rep<small>SLA bonus</small></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <!-- Shift CTA -->\n      <section class=\"shift-cta\">\n        <div class=\"clock-big\">\n          30:00\n          <small>shift length</small>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h3>It's 3:42 AM. The pager is ringing.</h3>\n          <p>Sit down for a live 30-minute support shift. 10 tickets, real-time, real LLMs. Score badges, refund money, lose sleep.</p>\n        </div>\n        <button class=\"start\">▶ Start shift now</button>\n      </section>\n\n    </div>\n  </main>\n</div>\n\n\n\n";
